ou named the linked binary \"shorten\":"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code-inline","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"shorten https://example.com"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"will yield a random short string. Just like typical shorteners do."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"code-inline","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"shorten https://example.com ohwow"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"will yield a "},{"type":"element","tag":"code-inline","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"mydomain.com/ohwow"}]},{"type":"text","value":" as the short link, meaning that we can customize the short string if we needed a memorable name."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"next-steps"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Next steps"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Now, this is pretty great as it's probably the easiest method of having a self-hosted link shortener, but if you want the fancy web UI there are some interesting ideas."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Inspired by NetlifyCMS, you could leverage their Git Gateway to \"push\" the commit containing the new redirect rules using a simple API."}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"I don't know if anyone else has tried it out yet, but it's certainly a good side project for the weekends."}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"netlify-shortener","depth":2,"text":"netlify-shortener","children":[{"id":"overview","depth":3,"text":"Overview"},{"id":"getting-it-to-work","depth":3,"text":"Getting it to work"},{"id":"trying-it-out","depth":3,"text":"Trying it out"}]},{"id":"next-steps","depth":2,"text":"Next steps"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"co